          <div class="guia-feat">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;">
              <div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:7px;background:rgba(168,85,247,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                <i class="bi bi-award-fill" style="color:#a855f7;font-size:0.85rem;"></i>
              </div>
              <span style="font-weight:700;font-size:0.85rem;">Selo Empresa Responsiva</span>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#555;font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Atualize os status dos candidatos para conquistar o selo público de empresa responsiva e atrair mais talentos.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="guia-feat">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;">
              <div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:7px;background:rgba(168,85,247,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                <i class="bi bi-magic" style="color:#a855f7;font-size:0.85rem;"></i>
              </div>
              <span style="font-weight:700;font-size:0.85rem;">Melhorar Vaga com IA</span>
            </div>
            <p style="color:#555;font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Refina automaticamente descrição, requisitos e benefícios da vaga ao criar ou editar.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════ CONTATO ═══════════════════ -->
    <div style="background:#0d0d0d;border:1px solid #1a1a1a;border-radius:16px;padding:36px;margin-top:48px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
      <!-- subtle glow -->
      <div style="position:absolute;right:-40px;top:-40px;width:180px;height:180px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(240,62,62,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;"></div>

      <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
        <div style="width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(240,62,62,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(240,62,62,0.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
          <i class="bi bi-chat-dots-fill" style="color:#f03e3e;font-size:1rem;"></i>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 style="font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1.05rem;">Não encontrou sua resposta?</h4>
          <p style="color:#444;margin:3px 0 0;font-size:0.83rem;">Envie sua dúvida — respondemos em até 24 horas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:22px;padding-bottom:20px;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1a1a;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;">
          <div style="width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#22c55e;"></div>
